## snippet to set up a hepmc hook

## this snippet is for fixed order ie NO shower

cd /Herwig/Analysis
create ThePEG::NLOHepMCFile HepMCFixedOrder HepMCAnalysis.so
set HepMCFixedOrder:PrintEvent 100000
set HepMCFixedOrder:Format GenEvent
set HepMCFixedOrder:Units GeV_mm
insert /Herwig/Generators/EventGenerator:AnalysisHandlers 0 HepMCFixedOrder


